{"tid":466754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞隆拿75萬人示威 要求釋放加泰領袖","createTime":"2017-11-13T01:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T04:28:36.000Z","uid":20058,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"65397b2a85a7883dd69ed1477444ca3f26ebf11a","tid":466754,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:02:40.000Z","msg":"約75萬人周六在西班牙巴塞隆拿舉行示威，要求釋放爭取獨立的加泰羅尼亞領袖。<br />\n<br />\n響應支持獨立組織號召的示威者，擠滿由沙灘直至巴塞地標Sagrada Familia教堂的整條碼頭大道(Avenue Marina)。他們在衣襟上戴上黃絲帶以示支持，而被囚的加泰領袖的家人則發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n今次示威遊行被視為加泰獨立運動是否仍得到民眾支持的指標。一位63歲的加泰居民說：「看看這些人，獨立運動仍堅決地進行。」他有信心主張獨立的政黨會贏得下月21日的地方選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171112/57448071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F57448071&d=ToY5HEM1M9s7pBlllVuXYv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a32868e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F57448071&h=3926b7ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171112/57448071</a>"},{"pid":"cfdbfd1618316f7a928b08471dfd217253c5f2e0","tid":466754,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:04:23.000Z","msg":"今天我，寒夜裡看雪飄過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcd0d791e91da2980f15b0d59dffdecd190c650","tid":466754,"uid":706,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:06:36.000Z","msg":"香港人: 下？比人捉走？話左唔好搞咁多架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲出黎示威救人？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要返工"},{"pid":"8b76ce34e1ece226bc22921562bb97d74e937f5f","tid":466754,"uid":16970,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquo